summary:
I am starting to rethink it was a good idea to binge watch the whole undertale series on an overnight 10 hour flight...
It was...
body:
I am starting to rethink it was a good idea to binge watch the whole undertale series on an overnight 10 hour flight…

It was still so worth it! Definitely one of my favourite series to this very day, I would love to see them play another long play through because they seemed to enjoy the undertale one a lot!

Especially how I nearly woke lots of people by attempting to hide my laughter. Coop and Doop are too funny for my own good 😂
